{"tid":1378962,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"機場示威十大好處 麻煩推post ！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:42:12.000Z","uid":153051,"like":176,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"cc125eef69fc9997bda81093f0db92e74205dabc","tid":1378962,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"1.機場係日日有最多唔同國家既人出現既地方<br />\n可以比佢地感受下 香港人示威既氣氛<br />\n你都知香港人 出名團結架啦<br />\n<br />\n2.機場入面班黑警做唔出d乜，<br />\n唔同元朗比佢地為所欲為 每一步都要好緊慎，<br />\n因為機場係主要通往其他國家既出入口<br />\n一陣<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">柒出國際</span></span> 又比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時又無得打9班記者 又無得扑9示威者<br />\n令唔識保護市民既黑警 懷疑自己既生存價值 <br />\n<br />\n3.機場店舖/櫃臺唔會因示威而落閘<br />\n(反映出香港人示威期間既秩序性高)<br />\n屌你政府話我地暴徒 <br />\n外國示威個d一早打撚爆晒商户玻璃+搶野啦on9<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">hk=和平+理性</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n4.由於香港機場遊行期間，<br />\n前往香港既旅客係 一定一定會知道發生緊咩事！<br />\n適用於 <blockquote>有睇過新聞</blockquote>，<br />\n但無特別去關注 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反送中</span></span>既遊客<br />\n<br />\n5.機場係24小時<br />\n到時班黑警又話拉又要鎖個陣，<br />\n每人揸一本passport話凖備去check in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎撚住個gip 你每一個都打開黎check？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我帶件黑衫去旅行唔犯法架可？</span></span><br />\n我就唔撚信你班黑警做撚埋地勤個份啦<br />\n<br />\n6.遊行人士可以實行輪班制度<br />\n攰既可以返屋企休息下 然後再黎過<br />\n夜晚就到收工或者休息過後既示威人士再度加入<br />\n玩殘班黑警既身體+心理 佢地點同香港人鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.機場連儂牆<br />\n相信每個人都會好好奇，<br />\n見到咁多人 都好願意花幾分鐘停留睇下發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.無位比黑警/政府入<br />\n坐係機場示威都想屈我地叫暴徒？<br />\n又想出動啲咩驅散人群？<br />\n比全世界人知道 到底香港政府有幾不堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.定期既機場集結 我相信政府無得唔回應<br />\n你係唔想比全世界既人知 我偏要幫你廣傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.屌你估你大陸真係大撚晒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望下出面個世界幾撚大先啦<br />\n唔係仲報導假新聞啊 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">畜龍小隊？成班收皮啦大陸佬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n但無論最後你地決定係邊度遊行都好，<br />\n我都會跟隨！<br />\n因為 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化！不割蓆！</span></span>"},{"pid":"bc35b1df7da42fe4084c42df6d9381a47eccb6f0","tid":1378962,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"96f58df06c46ddf24d53855792c630210ebab4d6","tid":1378962,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87640b91f4b8b0740752652648300a883e19e873","tid":1378962,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e7eec95b09bcae86dde1b10c53a2a1bd9b40ea7","tid":1378962,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c54083a80073b45455d2e791b2e4f5ae98f70c5","tid":1378962,"uid":159024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:14:04.000Z","msg":"唔好齋坐 仲要好好同旅客交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84866b9ea101a4c73ce04a3cf2bd57bb86699166","tid":1378962,"uid":136233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p