"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe47f1cf31f41d7166c713fc774fcb4e06cd7b19","tid":1378962,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61bd345113b246801901cbc924d241590527f30e","tid":1378962,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c02e44e08f717b86f27355a8ca1499e08130c5e9","tid":1378962,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"贊成<br />\nbtw<br />\n除左之前嘅尋親活動繼續令班狗社交受打擊，仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾佢地班仔女以佢老豆老母為恥</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>香港教育點失敗都唔會鼓吹暴力，班狗好多都有仔女讀緊中學、小學<br />\n</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">心理背景：<br />\n班黑警面對市民、其他公務員嘅唾罵都視若無睹、一錯在錯，原因有二：<br />\n1. 為左令屋企人有好生活、小朋友物質條件充裕，就算自己爛面，都要埋沒良心繼續攞份狗糧。<br />\n2. 街外人點睇唔理，反正自己生活圈子都係自己友圍爐，唔會覺得孤獨。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行動：<br />\n<em><br />\n<ins>9月2號開學日，我地打工仔同大學生一齊請假一天</ins>，於各個間中、小學門口派發黑警濫用暴力嘅海報單張，尤其係對冇防具嘅市民都打/開槍（常見於連儂牆嗰啲）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為左真實呈現，要彩色印刷A4 size</span></span><br />\n<ins><em>派傳單唔係鼓勵遊行乜乜乜，而係傳達真相，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以唔犯法</span>。</em></span></em></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">攻效：<br />\n如果小朋友/學生收到傳單，見到自己老豆老母嘅工作就係無差別打市民、向市民開槍，令到普通市民都無辜流血，一定好受打擊，返去問老豆老母點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">影響：<br />\n1. <ins>令黑警眾叛親離</ins>，連親生仔女都唾棄佢地，<ins>心理崩潰</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 令佢地<ins>小朋友心理受影響</ins>，令黑警要花多啲時間處理仔女情緒問題、修補關係，<ins>影響黑警於週末遊行嘅出勤率</ins>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 仔女為佢地黑警父母嘅惡行<ins>得到報應，警惕世人唔好為虎作倀、助紂為虐</ins>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<em>事前籌備：<br />\n1. 繼續整理過去6月至今嘅濫暴圖片，並持續收集嚟緊可能發生嘅濫暴素材。<br />\n2. 由於大量彩色列印需時，現時可以先行印刷已發生、fact check嘅濫用暴力素材，下次發夢亦可以先行派發測試反應。</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4488687eb124e37298a9f1c6f5e06eb160fa3b2b","tid":1378962,"uid":263200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d89e30e844a3b453a053d8b524d8660cf4f274","tid":1378962,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75801dce2280015e3ae246131e2668c256654d29","tid":1378962,"uid":136233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"其實個期係可以改<br />\n又唔係有不反對通知書<br />\n我覺得愈快愈好 <br />\n一係罷工個日去<br />\n一係今個weekend去<br />\n今日搞到咁又送頭<br />\n去機場唔使送頭！<br />\n又舒服 又有成效"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"5/8"},{"pid":"33c42f68bba86f5404003a31300bd944728e612f","tid":1378962,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c831adb9b8a820b57d34562df0e7bbe52351bf","tid":1378962,"uid":143008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"機場有好多大陸人..."},{"pid":"fa71f2fdebc7cafdf35bf90675fc861a842820fc","tid":1378962,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e3f5e247d2fd1bca80d6f20686010417858413","tid":1378962,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"但建議可以再稍微温和少少 會有更大效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}